    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Markdown-语法样例"><a href="#Markdown-语法样例" class="headerlink" title="Markdown 语法样例"></a>Markdown 语法样例</h1><blockquote><p>主要写些样例复习总结.<br>生活里面意外颇多，总是怕自己遗忘</p></blockquote><h2 id="各级标题"><a href="#各级标题" class="headerlink" title="各级标题"></a>各级标题</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section"># 一级标题 // 代表各级标题</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="引用"><a href="#引用" class="headerlink" title="引用"></a>引用</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; 名人名言 // 代表引用</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="代码块"><a href="#代码块" class="headerlink" title="代码块"></a>代码块</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="code">```开始</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">``` 结束</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="列表"><a href="#列表" class="headerlink" title="列表"></a>列表</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">* </span>1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">* </span>2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="链接"><a href="#链接" class="headerlink" title="链接"></a>链接</h2><p><a href="https://www.baidu.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">百度</a></p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[<span class="string">百度</span>](<span class="link">https://www.baidu.com</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="图片"><a href="#图片" class="headerlink" title="图片"></a>图片</h2><p><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/subject/l/public/s26851036.jpg" alt="盲视" title="盲视"></p><h2 id="任务列表"><a href="#任务列表" class="headerlink" title="任务列表"></a>任务列表</h2><ul><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox" checked> 吃饭</li><li>[] 睡觉</li><li>[] 打豆豆</li></ul><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">- </span>[x] 吃饭</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">- </span>[] 睡觉</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">- </span>[] 打豆豆</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
